    <item>
      <title>英国称超级富豪外国投资者威胁离开是虚张声势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/uk-budget-labour-calls-bluff-of-ultra-rich-foreigners-with-tax-changes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工党遭到了富人团体的猛烈抨击，他们希望避免在首份预算中受到严厉对待。本周，政府明确了选择：私募股权高管基本可以免于处罚，但非英国居民将多支付数十亿英镑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/uk-budget-labour-calls-bluff-of-ultra-rich-foreigners-with-tax-changes</guid>
